  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Fleet Supervisor (Delivery Route)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Government link company in the FMCG industry. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Fleet Supervisor to be part of their Warehouse team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the West.</strong></p><p>Duties of Fleet Supervisor:</p><ul><li>Plan and optimize efficient B2B delivery routes using transportation management systems.</li><li>Oversee daily delivery operations to ensure timely, accurate service and resolve any issues.</li><li>Manage and support drivers on routes, procedures, documentation, and safety protocols.</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety regulations and vehicle maintenance standards.</li><li>Monitor KPIs to improve delivery performance, route efficiency, and overall operations</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>At least 2 years of experience in fleet management and delivery route planning</li><li>Comfortable with 5 days rotating day shifts</li><li>Possess supervisory experience </li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume / cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li><li>EA License No. 19C9682</li><li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li></ul>",
